D:\DLIB\TOOLS\PYTHON\mkdir BUILD
D:\DLIB\TOOLS\PYTHON\BUILD\cmake -G "MinGW Makefiles" ..
D:\DLIB\TOOLS\PYTHON\BUILD\mingw32-make.exe all


Hello there,

